  <h1>Writing</h1>
  <p class="meta">Fiction by Michael Damon Bobbitt.</p>
  <div class="card">
    <h3>The Orb <span class="badge growing">in revision</span></h3>
    <p>
      A science-fiction novel, first in a planned universe that also connects to the games.
      Currently with early readers. Status updates and process notes will land in the
      <a href="/log/">devlog</a>.
    </p>
  </div>
  <p>
    The writing here is human. AI is used the way a good editor and a tireless research
    assistant would be. The voice, the choices, and the world are mine.
  </p>
</Base>
